title: ‘OnePlus 10’ leak suggests the non-Pro model will have 150W charging, no alert slider
content:
OnePlus has been playing coy about the standard OnePlus 10 while promoting the 10 Pro, but details are finally coming out. A fresh leak of the OnePlus 10 reveals that the phone will feature 150W charging and more.

more…

The post ‘OnePlus 10’ leak suggests the non-Pro model will have 150W charging, no alert slider appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: According to a new report, the OnePlus 10 will pack 150W fast charging, but will lack the brand's iconic alert slider.
